{"tid":1633943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚主題 重陽追悼義士","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:43:18.000Z","uid":86674,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c323f8caec2b08890291b2cc186ff5b0641134bb","tid":1633943,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"既然大家都想今晚出黎<br />\n又偏向和理非<br />\n<br />\n我建議今晚係商場哀悼義士<br />\n或者人鏈開手機燈之類既方式<br />\n<br />\n一黎等外媒記番起我地係有手足傷亡<br />\n唔好單方面話我地呢幾日破壞<br />\n同時再次宣傳港共係殺人政權<br />\n再加埋101 開槍，證明警暴<br />\n兩者混合，加強黑警殺人既印象<br />\n<br />\n二黎大家可以keep住有活動<br />\n保持政治能量<br />\n<br />\n三黎，我地真係要哀悼義士<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"d9707d59c2c084bde38a2714339a605ad6968683","tid":1633943,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:53:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a77a268b6bbb2b5a77039bf7253393b56f6b9fd","tid":1633943,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:54:15.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"891889a8eae3f302d029c5297127d00c27fe286a","tid":1633943,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"推到有人搞宗教集會"},{"pid":"992f6f15e5cf30bf8e6df0af0650695c80cfc24e","tid":1633943,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:56:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a283285c2fb4d459075a7cc58a1dc96c9b1ce5aa","tid":1633943,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"698812b186c6e0475d3f0b6a1db87441c29dcc33","tid":1633943,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:01:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9a294a709bd4991466891191828b47ac81fa973","tid":1633943,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:04:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n比個主題大家去拎名義呀"},{"pid":"e167032bb4e4b915832ae96bf95b90ce55d2171b","tid":1633943,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"rep